or.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22110309/IMG_7740-1536x1025.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22110309/IMG_7740-2048x1367.jpg 2048w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22110309/IMG_7740-696x465.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22110309/IMG_7740-1068x713.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22110309/IMG_7740-1920x1281.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22110309/IMG_7740-629x420.jpg 629w\"></a></p><h3>Calibration</h3><p>After the build, I was prepared for the long haul on the calibration process of the Tuo. I downloaded the Elite app and it quickly paired with the trainer and updated the firmware up to date, good to go.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22135654/Screen-Shot-2021-03-22-at-1.56.13-PM.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22135654/Screen-Shot-2021-03-22-at-1.56.13-PM.png\" alt=\"Elite Apps \" width=\"2446\" height=\"2522\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2446px) 100vw, 2446px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22135654/Screen-Shot-2021-03-22-at-1.56.13-PM.png\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22135654/Screen-Shot-2021-03-22-at-1.56.13-PM.png 2446w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22135654/Screen-Shot-2021-03-22-at-1.56.13-PM-291x300.png 291w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor